                          <locus from="67">67</locus>, <locus from="114" to="119">114—119</locus>,
                          <locus from="127">127</locus>, <locus from="128">128</locus>, and <locus from="153" to="155">153—155</locus>. The quires, signed with letters, were
                        at least 16 in number, but the first two are lost, and the third and last
                        are imperfect. There are from 14 to 18 lines in each page.</p>
                    </item>
